7 OFFICE OF EDUCATION PARTNERSHIPS
8 Sec. 401. From the funds appropriated in part 1 for family and
9 community engagement, the department shall, at a minimum, do all of
10 the following:
11 (a) Establish or partner with family engagement centers across
12 this state to increase parent and guardian involvement in their
13 child's education.
14 (b) Ensure translation and interpretation services are
15 available and implemented pursuant to department guidance.
16 (c) Partner with intermediate school districts to assist in
17 getting information and resources to their constituent districts.
18 (d) Develop an early literacy engagement plan to help parents
19 or guardians become involved in their child's education.
